mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"可能有自知之明姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果冇翻譯 到時聽唔明佢地講乜亂判就唔好啦"},{"pid":"d7089c5ac15d5364714929f9af3375f5577d6aff","tid":789326,"uid":116390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有持碩士學位的人士，以英語表示英文程度不好，法官不接納其理由，不獲豁免出任陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書讀得越多個人就越濕鳩,自古皆準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>可能有自知之明姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果冇翻譯 到時聽唔明佢地講乜亂判就唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n咁碩士都唔一定英文好ge"},{"pid":"8ea12dcf2cf0af795e0e2d84eb7dd0968d794ca6","tid":789326,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"條新女如果趕得切同佢結婚就可以做大贏家 而家賭錯郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eba594f59bdd5fabfab91cc58c3a04f4ff26368","tid":789326,"uid":198622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e29572f8afe11bf5f43e4338937828877c86ebef","tid":789326,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca323592c6eca44baf1b4ad92daa49ab41baaadd","tid":789326,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被告知道妻子平時會用車，遂於其間拆開瑜伽波排氣口伺機殺人，但殊不知當天次女剛巧放假，故被告未料車上有其他乘客。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當聽到主控提及這點時，於犯人欄內的被告除下眼鏡，雙眼緊閉流淚，臉部亦通紅。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}